    "messy": false,
    "notes": "The fossil choice -- the game's first true branch. Taking either fossil sets its GOT flag and hides its ball; the Super Nerd then battles you (EVENT_BEAT_MT_MOON_EXIT_SUPER_NERD) and takes the OTHER fossil (value 5 hides the remaining ball). FOSSIL_1 is the Dome ball, FOSSIL_2 the Helix ball. Either branch ends with both balls gone. The four floor trainers are independent beat-bits."
